name: Fake Internet Money
description:
Fake Internet Money is buying up the entire supply of Steve Pikelny's incredible collection, "Fake Internet Money" created for ArtBlocks.

The goal is to make the collection of this artwork a reserve currency of the world. 

Not only is the artwork incredibly detailed, meticulously created, but conceptually it is the strongest work produced yet in the digital space on the intangible hypocrisy of the concept of monetary value. 

By amassing an enormous collection of Fake Internet Money, we will simultaneously make it "real". 

See: https://www.artblocks.io/project/152
payDisclosure:
They money you are contributing will be put into a treasury, managed by a DAO, and used to purchase Steve Pikelny's "Fake Internet Money" with the goal of creating a new global currency. 

This is an art project with serious real goals. It is not affiliated with Steve Pikelny.
